
novels_lstm
  Copyright (c) Original Authors: Jason Brownlee, 山陰少年
----------------------------------------------------------

[1] Text Generation With LSTM Recurrent Neural Networks in Python with Keras
Jason Brownlee
https://www.cnblogs.com/jclian91/p/9863848.html

[2] RNN入門（三）利用LSTM生成旅遊點評
山陰少年
https://www.cnblogs.com/jclian91/p/9863848.html

本人參考兩位作者的步驟，完成 LSTM 練習，並整理為本程式碼之中的 novels_lstm， 在此保留原作者完整資訊，且聲明在這部分本人無任何權利，所有權利應歸屬兩位原作者。

The code in novels_lstm are my practice which reference are Jason Brownlee's and 山陰少年's blog article.
Therefore, preserve all information for authors.



